name: .VDS File Extension
summary: Learn about .VDS files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can open a VDS file with any program in the SAP 3D Visual Enterprise suite (Windows), including 3D Visual Enterprise Generator, Author, Navigator, and Viewer. These programs are paid programs, which are available only within the 3D Visual Enterprise suite.
